    <h3>Warranty</h3>

    <p>Instela Maestros warranty the Jobs they do for seven days. Instela offers no additional warranty.</p>

    <h3>Private Engagement</h3>

    <p>Instela Maestros are assigned to Jobs on the basis of availability and location. A Customer may not be assigned the same Maestro each time they Post a Job.</p>

    <p>As a Customer you agree not to privately offer jobs to Maestros you have previously engaged with through Instela. As a Maestro you agree not to accept or solicit for jobs that are offered to you by Customers you have previously worked for through Instela.</p>

    <p>Instela reserves the right to terminate the Accounts of Users who enter into private engagements.</p>

